      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it sounds scary but i get these really bad migraines all the time and usually they just pass if i take some extra ibuprofen and rest in a dark room. honestly the ER is gonna cost me a fortune and i feel like i just need to sleep it off. are you sure it's not just a complex migraine flare up? it kinda feels like the ones i've had before just way more intense.",
